comments: Jen is the best teacher I have had in College. Her classes are informative but fun, and she is helpful and fun outside of the classroom.
Prof. Jen is cool, she\'s very approachable and engaging in class. Her teaching style makes me WANT to go to class. By far the hippest faculty member of the department.
I like this teacher a lot. She makes her classes interesting and willl go out of her way to help you if you hav a problem.

I love this professor. Her classes are always interesting, and she\'s very accessible. It seems that the students that don\'t like her class are the know-it-alls that want to teach the class themselves. Get over yourselves.

Ms. Suwak doesn\'t seem to know what she\'s talking about 99% of the time. Her course "teaching" is a total crap shoot, (choosing "Nick and Nora\'s infinite Playlist" as a "required viewing" for Directing class???) Doesn\'t seem to take her job seriously
Great Teacher. She is sort of a neo-hippie ;). I love her whole attitude. The kind of teacher you are pals with but still demands that you learn the material. uses great media to illustrate points.
